	"keywords": "javascript, Reasonml, React, Functional Programming, Web Development",
	"description": "Are you using React [https://reactjs.org/] to build user interfaces? Well, I am\ntoo. And now, you’ll learn why you should write your React applications using\nReasonML\n[https://medium.freecodecamp.org/learn-reasonml-by-building-tic-tac-toe-in-react-334203dd513c]\n.\n\nReact is a pretty cool way to write user interfaces. But, could we make it even\ncooler? Better?\n\nTo make it better, we need to identify its problems first. So, what is the main\nproblem of React as a JavaScript library?\n\nReact wasn’t in",
